Subject: How To Get Started In Cosplay
Description: Have you seen a lot of con goers dressed up in fabulous costumes? Would you like to join in on the fun? Feeling a little clueless on how to start or maybe a bit intimidated? We will talk about techniques to make a costume, sources of inspiration, how to choose a character, and trying to keep it all in a budget.  Speakers include:Jennifer Skwarski - Track: Cosplay  - Duration: 1 hour
